name: To Bop or Not to Bop

settings.description: B.O.P = Bouncing On Pinheads (though Wigglers have very round heads) - Prod. Code: 084A, Rel: 9/1/22, 6:00pm, Accidental Rel: 6/?/22
what's up with all these spinning spiny shells? well... be glad ya aren't playing the NES and SNES version here, for ya can't stomp them in them versions of SMB3, but here? you can!
Cannons to the LEFT of me.. BOOTS! BOOTS! Bullets to the RIGHT o' me.. BOMBS! BOMBS! I'm going mad.. it's the desert madness! AAAAA! -- at the end of room 2, the warp exit is under the centre block.
Hurry up and collect the clocks before time runs out!
In Oct. 2021, I made a level called "Woody Purple Fiends," but due to a glitch, I changed the title by "Black Killer Holes." Now there's a game crash there, so I did some cleanup to fix everything.
Mario enters a random airship in the way of his journey to his house. He could have just walked around, but hes Mario. What do you expect? Reissue of Fall Away Frieghts #109B, 12/6/22 - 9:20am
